steps.description:
The shrimp should be in cold or ice water when you peel it. To peel the shrimp, just pull off the head, if it's still attached, along with the legs. Start with the head end and pull off the outer shell. You can decide whether you want to leave the tail tip on for presentation, or take it off for eating convenience. Place the shells in a plastic bag and seal it shut to throw them out. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/94/Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/v4-459px-Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/94/Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/v4-759px-Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

If you want to use the shells to make shellfish stock later, just seal them in a plastic bag and place it in your freezer. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8a/Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/v4-459px-Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8a/Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/v4-759px-Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

You can leave the shell on to keep some of the flavor, though this will make the shrimp a bit harder to eat. If you want to do this, you should cut the outer edge of the shrimp's back with kitchen scissors, so you can devein the shrimp easily. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7f/Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-459px-Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7f/Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-759px-Prepare-Shrimp-Scampi-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}
